## Workflow

```text
{%- for skill in ordered_skills %}
{%- set transitions = by_skill[skill] -%}
{%- set all_froms = [] -%}{%- set all_tos = [] -%}
{%- for t in transitions -%}
{%- set _ = all_froms.append(t["from"]) -%}
{%- set _ = all_tos.append(t["to"]) -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- set entry_candidates = [] -%}
{%- for f in all_froms -%}
{%- if f not in all_tos -%}
{%- set _ = entry_candidates.append(f) -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- if not entry_candidates -%}
{%- set entry = transitions[0]["from"] -%}
{%- else -%}
{%- set entry = entry_candidates[0] -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- set chain = [entry] -%}
{%- set current = entry -%}
{%- for _ in range(20) -%}
{%- set nexts = [] -%}
{%- for t in transitions -%}
{%- if t["from"] == current and t["to"] not in chain and t["to"] not in terminal_statuses -%}
{%- set _ = nexts.append(t["to"]) -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- if nexts -%}
{%- set nxt = nexts[0] -%}
{%- set _ = chain.append(nxt) -%}
{%- set current = nxt -%}
{%- else -%}
{%- set done_steps = [] -%}
{%- for t in transitions -%}
{%- if t["from"] == current and t["to"] == "done" -%}
{%- set _ = done_steps.append(t["to"]) -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- if done_steps -%}
{%- set _ = chain.append("done") -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- break -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- set primary_edges = [] -%}
{%- for i in range(chain | length - 1) -%}
{%- set _ = primary_edges.append((chain[i], chain[i+1])) -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- set annotations = {"loopback": [], "parking": [], "cancellation": [], "failure": [], "skip": []} -%}
{%- for t in transitions -%}
{%- set frm = t["from"] -%}
{%- set to = t["to"] -%}
{%- set is_primary = false -%}
{%- for pe in primary_edges -%}
{%- if pe[0] == frm and pe[1] == to -%}
{%- set is_primary = true -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- if not is_primary -%}
{%- if to == "cancelled" -%}
{%- set _ = annotations["cancellation"].append(frm) -%}
{%- elif to == "fail" -%}
{%- set _ = annotations["failure"].append(frm) -%}
{%- elif to == "done" -%}
{%- set _ = annotations["skip"].append(frm) -%}
{%- elif to == "backlog" -%}
{%- set _ = annotations["parking"].append(frm ~ " → " ~ to) -%}
{%- elif to in chain and frm in chain and chain.index(to) < chain.index(frm) -%}
{%- set _ = annotations["loopback"].append(frm ~ " → " ~ to) -%}
{%- else -%}
{%- set _ = annotations["parking"].append(frm ~ " → " ~ to) -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
/{{ skill }}    {{ chain | join(" → ") }}
{%- if annotations["loopback"] -%}
{%- for item in annotations["loopback"] %}
          (loopback: {{ item }})
{%- endfor -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- if annotations["parking"] -%}
{%- for item in annotations["parking"] %}
          (parking: {{ item }})
{%- endfor -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- if annotations["cancellation"] -%}
          (cancellation: {{ annotations["cancellation"] | join("/") }} → cancelled)
{%- endif -%}
{%- if annotations["failure"] -%}
          (failure: {{ annotations["failure"] | join("/") }} → fail)
{%- endif -%}
{%- if annotations["skip"] -%}
          (skip: {{ annotations["skip"] | join("/") }} → done)
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor %}

Terminal states: {{ terminal_statuses | join(" · ") }}
```

## Extensions

Project-specific guidance and accumulated knowledge layer onto skills and agents at runtime:

- **Lessons** — `~/Claude/{project}/lessons/*.md`. Authored by `/learn` after retrospectives; loaded into every skill at render time via the lessons context loader.
- **Skill overrides** — `~/Claude/{project}/_booping/skill_<name>.md`. Loaded into the matching skill at render time via the extra-instructions context loader.
- **Agent overrides** — `~/Claude/{project}/_booping/agent_booping-<name>.md`. Loaded into the matching agent at render time via the extra-instructions context loader.

## Hard rules

- **`/help` never writes files.** If the user needs scaffolding, hand off to `/install`.

